There are all these things that I could want to do as I'm trying to, like, you know, sort

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:13.279
of deploy this app and, you know, add some horsepower.

00:03:13.679 --> 00:03:17.039
These are, like, hard, scary, big questions.

00:03:17.039 --> 00:03:21.240
And really what they boil down to is, you know, is my deployment sophisticated enough?

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:24.679
Am I doing it for real or not?

00:03:24.679 --> 00:03:29.639
Of course, I then, you know, did what I sometimes do when I'm procrastinating, which was I started

00:03:29.639 --> 00:03:33.399
watching Star Wars just because, you know, why not do that?

00:03:33.399 --> 00:03:38.039
Y'all might know this guy, green, big ears, talks funny.

