And I thought this was really appropriate, right?

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:51.119
Like, if you just sub in the word, like, sophistication here, this is a great way to

00:03:51.119 --> 00:03:54.600
think of why do we care about deploying shiny apps?

00:03:54.600 --> 00:03:56.880
And, of course, we care because we want to increase value.

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:58.559
